## 🎨 Design System & Theme

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| **Font** | `Plus Jakarta Sans` (Google Fonts) — weights 400–800 |
| **CSS Framework** | Tailwind CSS (CDN) |
| **Background** | `bg-slate-50` (#f8fafc) — light icy grey |
| **Primary Accent** | `#c00000` — DepEd Red (buttons, active sidebar, badges) |
| **Secondary Accents** | Blue (#3b82f6), Emerald (#10b981), Orange (#f97316) |
| **Text** | Slate-800 primary, Slate-400/500 secondary |
| **Border Radius** | Extremely rounded: `rounded-[2.5rem]` / `rounded-[3rem]` cards |
| **Shadow Style** | `shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50` — soft, diffused |
| **Typography Style** | `font-extrabold`, `tracking-tight`, `italic` accents, `uppercase tracking-widest` labels |

### Color Coding by Section
- **Legislative District 1** → Blue (`text-blue-600`, `bg-blue-50`)
- **Legislative District 2** → Emerald (`text-emerald-600`, `bg-emerald-50`)
- **Serviceable assets** → Emerald
- **Unserviceable assets** → Orange
- **Primary actions** → DepEd Red `#c00000`

---

## 🏗️ Layout Structure

### Dashboard (`/dashboard`)
Two-column layout:

| Section | Description |
|---|---|
| **Sidebar** (fixed, 288px) | Logo + nav + user profile with logout |
| **Main Content** (scrollable) | Header → Stats Cards → Quick Entry → District Portfolio |

**Sidebar sections:**
1. **Brand** — DepEd logo + "DepEd ZC" + "Asset Management" subtitle
2. **Dashboard** link (active state: red bg, bold)
3. **Configuration** — Inventory Setup link
4. **LD 1** — Quadrant 1.1 (3 Dist), Quadrant 1.2 (2 Dist)
5. **LD 2** — Quadrant 2.1 (3 Dist), Quadrant 2.2 (4 Dist)
6. **User Profile** — Avatar initial + email + "Admin" badge + logout button

**Main content sections:**
1. **Header** — "Welcome, Admin!" + date card (top-right)
2. **3 Stat Cards** — Total Assets / Good Condition / Pasira/Damaged
3. **Quick Asset Entry** — Inline form with search bar, dropdowns, and ➕ button
4. **District Summary Portfolio** — 4 quadrant cards in a 2×2 grid

### Inventory Setup (`/inventory-setup`)
Single-column, centered wizard with **3 steps**:
- **Step 1:** Action picker (Add New / Edit-Update) — 2 big cards
- **Step 2:** Category picker (Schools / Districts / Items) — 3 cards in a row
- **Step 3:** Dynamic form rendered via JavaScript based on selection

### Auth Pages (`/` login, `/register`)
Centered card layout on a radial gradient background (`circle at top right, #ffffff, #f1f5f9`):
- Red accent bar at top of card (`h-1.5 bg-deped-red`)
- Footer bar: "Division of Zamboanga City • Inventory 1.0"
- Registration includes **OTP verification flow** via Alpine.js

---

## ✨ Animations & Transitions

| Animation | Where Used | CSS |
|---|---|---|
| **Fade-in on load** | Body / page entry | `@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; translateY(10px) } to { opacity:1; translateY(0) } }` 0.5s ease-out |
| **Fade-in + scale** | Inventory Setup step transitions | `@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; scale(0.98) } to { opacity:1; scale(1) } }` 0.3s ease-out |
| **Hover lift** | Stat cards, district cards | `hover:-translate-y-2` with `transition-all duration-300` |
| **Icon scale on hover** | Emoji icons in cards | `group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform` |
| **Shadow amplify on hover** | Cards | `hover:shadow-2xl` |
| **Border highlight on hover** | District cards, setup cards | `hover:border-blue-200` / `hover:border-[#c00000]` |
| **Button press** | Submit buttons | `active:scale-95` / `active:scale-[0.98]` |
| **Sidebar slide** | Mobile toggle | `transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out` + `-translate-x-full` toggle |
| **Sidebar overlay** | Backdrop blur | `bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm` with opacity transition 0.3s |
| **Auth button hover** | Login/register | `translateY(-2px)` + `box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -5px rgba(192,0,0,0.3)` + `brightness(1.1)` |
| **Inner glow on hover** | District card stats area | `group-hover:bg-blue-50/30` / `group-hover:bg-emerald-50/30` |

