## Key Design Patterns

- **Ultra-rounded cards** (`rounded-[2.5rem]`+) give a soft, premium feel
- **Uppercase micro-labels** (`text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest`) for form labels and section headers
- **Emoji as icons** (📊🏢✅⚠️📍⚙️🏫📦🔍) — no icon library dependency
- **Color-coded districts** — blue for LD1, emerald for LD2
- **Responsive sidebar** — fixed on desktop, slide-in overlay on mobile with backdrop blur
- **No password login** — email-only auth, matching the approval-based registration flow
